<headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 01 at 10:12AM EDT  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...ELEVATED FIRE WEATHER CONCERNS TODAY...
Moderate to severe drought across the region has resulted in
elevated fire weather concerns for today. Relative humidity
values will drop to near 35 percent this afternoon with northwest
gusts between 15 and 25 mph. Any fire that ignites will have the
potential to rapidly spread in these conditions.</description>
